    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth engine and transmission, and it has been meticulously maintained with a full service history. Buyers can expect a collector-quality vehicle that requires zero investment and offers a like-new driving experience.",
